Class InstructionPattern

java.lang.Object
instructionpattrns.InstructionPattern
Direct Known Subclasses:
AddressInstructionPattern, NopInstructionPattern, RegisterInstructionPattern, ScalarInstructionPattern
public abstract class InstructionPattern extends Object
Abstract base class for instruction patterns, with functionality for matching with an actual instruction.

    • matches

      public final boolean matches(ghidra.program.model.listing.Instruction inst)
      Checks if the given instruction matches an instruction pattern. This is the main function to call for matching; it will call the specific implementation logic internally.
      Parameters:
      inst - The instruction to check against the instruction pattern.
      Returns:
      true if the instruction matches the instruction pattern, false otherwise.
